description:
First tear: Geili Mei (played by Zhou Dongyu), a beautiful girl suffering from bone cancer, has not been frightened by the disease. She infects every patient in the hospital with her optimistic spirit. Under her inspiration, the hospital, which should have been gloomy and melancholy, became like a paradise on earth. On this day, the rich second-generation Youyou (played by Li Zhiting) who suffered from brain cancer was admitted to the hospital. His despair and anger were quickly dispelled by the smiles on Limei and the children, and the hospital became the last happy station in their lives;

                                The second tear: The Lutheran Conservatory of Music, which has cultivated countless talents, is facing bankruptcy. In order to save the school and fulfill his late wife's wish, Principal Chen decided to call the graduating students back to school to hold a concert. Ding Dake (played by Simon Yam), who had been in love with his classmate, the now internationally famous violinist Yang Lin (played by Gigi Leung), was ordered to invite Yang Lin to attend;

                                The third tear: Chen Sheng (played by Dou Xiao), a young man from the bottom, finally achieved something in his career after hard work. When he was about to marry his girlfriend Xiaocai (played by Chen Qiaoen) who he had been in love with for many years, an accident suddenly happened.
